sh Notification</p><p data-block-id=\"3defe89e-0791-4760-80ef-6058d12d4775\">&lt;put your video and screenshot&gt;</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"7cacbff0-6097-4577-8bea-2670eefceb05\"></h2><p data-block-id=\"3a86b5ec-38da-4400-83d2-ef1024cbe6c9\"></p><p data-block-id=\"12295416-ce37-4b1f-ae9c-e422707d5254\"></p><p data-block-id=\"8e9aac87-b7ff-4f0e-b9c9-0178d8f76e42\"></p><p data-block-id=\"1fba7422-3f0f-475f-a3cd-ed72e33bce4f\"></p><p data-block-id=\"acd97665-43b1-498b-89ca-e66b24c0a68f\"></p><p data-block-id=\"490a489a-2a58-4dc9-96ea-9e5cc09fc8be\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Metrobank Online Banking","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Metrobank Online Banking","Slug":"metrobank-online-banking","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"352f5147-4fbd-48a9-904a-b0c8ab9c977b\"><img data-block-id=\"b74227c2-cc02-4d7c-9062-434639898b1a\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/images (3).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"233\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" style=\"width:233px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"8d96d958-de6d-4973-ac24-ec13f2db435c\">Metropolitan Bank and Trust Company (Metrobank) adalah salah satu bank terbesar dan paling tepercaya di Filipina. Metrobank Online Banking, tersedia melalui situs web dan aplikasi selulernya (<strong>Metrobank Online</strong>), memberdayakan nasabah untuk mengelola keuangan mereka dengan mudah, aman, dan fleksibel.</p><p data-block-id=\"db5ac7a2-6bd1-4c5f-a1ca-bdaec795cdab\">Metrobank Online menawarkan beragam layanan, termasuk transfer dana, pembayaran tagihan, manajemen akun, pelacakan investasi, dan lainnya. Dirancang untuk pengguna perorangan dan bisnis, platform ini memenuhi kebutuhan perbankan modern, memberikan pengalaman digital yang aman dan lancar.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">Fitur</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"926\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\";max-width:926px;width:926px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:463px;\"><col style=\"width:463px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"402452f7-7a96-45f3-856a-beec3466fb7a\">Kode Channel</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"648b3370-267a-47a5-bafd-0cfb81370827\">METROBANK_ONLINE_BANKING</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"e924926f-9906-4496-af4a-b319c2a2c8d4\">Mata Uang</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"89cc4585-3036-4f0a-847a-3a0f634c0a27\">PHP</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"6598736d-d850-48ae-b29e-ba649fb13157\">Jumlah Minimum</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"f5c1c704-b8ae-4d25-8fd5-2694332b973d\">1.00</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom